cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with object recognition and pose estimation using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves manifold learning and regression, which are relevant to robotics (cs.RO), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM). However, since the focus is on computer vision, cs.CV is the most likely category, followed by cs.RO and cs.LG.
